<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Mosquera Counseling — Financial Portal | TurnkeyCFO</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{--tk-navy:#00263A;--tk-navy-mid:#003A56;--tk-green:#00C85A;--tk-green-bright:#05DD69;--tk-ice:#DAE1E9;--tk-bg-light:#F2F5F8;--tk-white:#FFFFFF;--tk-text:#0D1F2D;--tk-text-soft:#36576A;--tk-text-muted:#7A909F}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--tk-bg-light) 0%,var(--tk-white) 100%);color:var(--tk-text);min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.shell{max-width:600px;text-align:center;padding:48px 24px}
.eyebrow{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tk-text-muted);margin-bottom:12px}
h1{font-size:28px;font-weight:800;color:var(--tk-navy);margin-bottom:8px}
h1 span{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--tk-green),var(--tk-green-bright));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text}
.sub{font-size:15px;color:var(--tk-text-soft);margin-bottom:32px;line-height:1.6}
.card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.88);border:1px solid rgba(0,38,58,0.08);border-radius:20px;box-shadow:0 12px 32px rgba(7,47,69,0.08);padding:28px;margin-bottom:20px}
.status{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:8px 16px;background:var(--tk-bg-light);border-radius:10px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--tk-text)}
.dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--tk-green);animation:pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:0.4}}
.footer{margin-top:40px;font-size:12px;color:var(--tk-text-muted)}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="shell">
<div class="eyebrow">TurnkeyCFO · Financial Portal</div>
<h1>Mosquera Counseling <span>Portal</span></h1>
<p class="sub">Your dedicated financial command center is being configured. Monthly dashboards, financial statements, and CFO insights will appear here.</p>
<div class="card">
<div class="status"><div class="dot"></div> Portal Setup In Progress</div>
</div>
<div class="footer">TurnkeyCFO · Confidential · 2026</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
